data.description: Lovely one story, three bedroom home on a premium corner lot.  The open-concept design integrates the living, dining and kitchen areas with hardwood flooring throughout, creating an ideal space for both relaxation and entertaining.  The owner's suite with recessed ceiling, walk in closet, walk in shower and double vanity in owner's bath.  Covered front porch, covered rear porch with a large back yard is perfect for entertaining  Low city taxes and no MUD.  Carlson Place is ideally situated close to the vibrant Georgetown Square with festivals, shopping and dining.  Centrally located to 130 and I35 for easy commute.  Come see today!  **All information deemed reliable, but not guaranteed. Agent and Buyer to verify all information.
